{"tid":623420,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"90後股神渾水話毛記落到3蚊可以入貨","createTime":"2018-04-10T03:44:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T19:02:43.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"c3d19b61664f970cbc148daf8c17125200fd28b2","tid":623420,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:44:27.000Z","msg":"渾水認為，毛記的業務性質與Hypebeast（8359）的相近，同樣講求「食腦」有創意，而Hypebeast過去1年多的業績持續改善，股價也持續上揚，因此相信只要毛記管理層能夠持續推出新搞作，多舉辦如《東方昇特異功能救香港》的表演，自然能加強盈利能力、推高估值，故此當毛記見3元水平時，他會積極考慮買一注毛記股票，「押注3位『腦細』將來成功」。Hypebeast最近一期業績的年化純利為5,614萬元，以今日收市價0.85元計，對應的市盈率為30.3倍，遠低於毛記的市盈率。"},{"pid":"fec60985cf94d5c0cc2edfc2db239f82cea35439","tid":623420,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:48:21.000Z","msg":"Gun"},{"pid":"8bda2efb0413b3672deeee4a9283248fc7f2a0bd","tid":623420,"uid":38737,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T03:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/114920_3eaad89a5abeda0db5d435f06d04a94d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F114920_3eaad89a5abeda0db5d435f06d04a94d.png&h=d1a9c535&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe28fd3b530ea361b16531bc44f4ae9b48deaed9","tid":623420,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:46:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc579e288cab690996b60e96d2ef297ff7743d4","tid":623420,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:50:17.000Z","msg":"留名鞭屍"},{"pid":"a9d39cd6174c61a134f78cc606604ab6aff3ab26","tid":623420,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T11:08:54.000Z","msg":"20180411 收巿報$2.840"},{"pid":"dc99a1823e6ffb423d108c18293a1bc9331af4be","tid":623420,"uid":11969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9d39cd6174c61a134f78cc606604ab6aff3ab26","tid":623420,"ui